To make him different from T.O.M. my character, Gash, was raised among orcs and was a member of a raiding party that was chased into a desert. The warband, having lost their original pursuers, was then attacked by undead. The rest of raiders died (and became undead), and my half-orc was offered a deal by a being that would let him get his vengeance and put his warband to rest in exchange